  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/CoreMedia\/kCMTextMarkupGenericFontName_SmallCapital\ncrawled: 2026-03-10T23:50:17Z\n---\n\n# kCMTextMarkupGenericFontName_SmallCapital\n\n**Global Variable**\n\nA font with lowercase letters set as small capital letters.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nlet kCMTextMarkupGenericFontName_SmallCapital: CFString\n```\n\n## Font Names\n\n- **kCMTextMarkupGenericFontName_Default**: The default font.\n- **kCMTextMarkupGenericFontName_Serif**: A font with serifs.\n- **kCMTextMarkupGenericFontName_SansSerif**: A font without serifs.\n- **kCMTextMarkupGenericFontName_Monospace**: A monospaced font with or without serifs.\n- **kCMTextMarkupGenericFontName_MonospaceSerif**: A monospaced font with serifs.\n- **kCMTextMarkupGenericFontName_MonospaceSansSerif**: A monospaced font without serifs.\n- **kCMTextMarkupGenericFontName_ProportionalSerif**: A proportional font with serifs.\n- **kCMTextMarkupGenericFontName_ProportionalSansSerif**: A proportional font without serifs.\n- **kCMTextMarkupGenericFontName_Casual**: A casual font.\n- **kCMTextMarkupGenericFontName_Cursive**: A cursive font.\n- **kCMTextMarkupGenericFontName_Fantasy**: A fantasy font.\n\n",
